public class UsersProfilePage
extends org.apache.wicket.markup.html.WebPage

The page provides some basic operation on the UsersProfile bean.

  • Form to edit and add UsersProfile with ajax buttons
  • AjaxFallbackDefaultDataTable to show and enable operations on the UsersProfile
